1
00:00:00,050 --> 00:00:06,197
NightRx is a privacy-preserving healthcare credential system built on Midnight.

2
00:00:06,197 --> 00:00:09,000
A clinic issues a private credential.

3
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:12,263
The patient generates a zero-knowledge proof.

4
00:00:12,263 --> 00:00:17,618
And the pharmacy verifies it on-chain — without ever seeing the diagnosis.

